{"title":"优秀——一位新兵的话","authors":["曹士飞"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":6,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"优秀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一位新兵的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士　曹士飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人向我来祝贺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人握住我的手；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新战友瞅我胸前花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老战友向我直点头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说我新兵打得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头一次打靶得优秀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有指导员站一旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞅着我微笑不开口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打靶回来他叫住我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领我到“光荣室”里头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，光荣榜上光荣像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特等射手排了一大溜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个，百发子弹百发中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个，朝鲜战场有名的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狙击手……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，头次打靶戴红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是孩子学迈步才开头！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}